author: MAX
install_msg:
Thanks for installing.
⚠️This cog require that you have dislash installed to work.⚠️
if you have any question, you can find me in #testing in <https://discord.gg/red>.
Once you load this cog, it will replace the invite in core with this one. on unload you will need to restart your bot to get the old way back.

This cog uses core's `inviteset` to add permission level. To set permission level use `[p]inviteset perms`.
description: A cog with your invite link that has the new buttons.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store any data.
